hyperv: Add handler for RNDIS_STATUS_NETWORK_CHANGE event

The RNDIS_STATUS_NETWORK_CHANGE event is received after the Hyper-V host
sleep or hibernation. We refresh network at this time.
MS-TFS: 135162

